{{main article|1962年飓风阿尔玛}}
8月26日，[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]东南近海的[[东风波|东风波]]发展成热带低气压。气旋沿海岸线北上，并在上空[[反气旋|反气旋]]的影响下增强。8月27日，热带低气压开始朝东北移动，并于当天在佛罗里达州和[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]边界以东约240公里海域强化成热带风暴并获名“阿尔玛”（{{lang|en|Alma}}），成为[[1941年大西洋飓风季|1941年]]后各大西洋飓风季形成日期最晚的首场风暴。风暴沿[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]海岸线平行移动并稳步增强，于8月28日在北卡罗莱纳州[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）近海成为飓风。虽然飓风的移动路线距陆地很近，但北卡罗莱纳州[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]][[纳格斯黑德_(北卡罗莱纳州)|纳格斯黑德]]（{{lang|en|Nags Head}}）所测最强阵风时速也只达到85公里。<ref name="mwr" />阵风将[[哈特拉斯_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯]]（{{lang|en|Hatteras}}）的一根电线杆刮倒，导致全镇三分之一地区停电一小时<ref>{{cite report | author = Weddle | publisher = National Hurricane Center | work = Weather Bureau Office Cape Hatteras, North Carolina | date = 1962-08-28 | title = The Passage of Tropical Storm Alma at WBO Cape Hatteras NC on August 28, 1962 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051755/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshhat.gif | accessdate = 2013-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshhat.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。哈特拉斯出现0.91米的风暴潮，导致一定程度的[[海蚀|侵蚀]]<ref name="mwr" />。全美以哈特拉斯角降水最多，达264毫米<ref>{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | date = 2009-09-28 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | title = Hurricane Alma – August 25–31, 1962 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002430/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alma1962.html | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alma1962.html }}</ref>，北卡罗莱纳州的损失数额约为3.5万美元<ref name="mwr" />。

经过[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]后，阿尔玛进一步增强，在[[南塔克特|南塔克特]]以南约135公里洋面达到风力时速155公里的最高强度<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。虽已达二级飓风标准，但气旋始终未能呈现出层次分明的[[风眼|风眼]]。受行经海域水温降低影响<ref name="bos" />，飓风在逼近新英格兰期间迅速减弱<ref name="mwr" />。风暴在[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]]和[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]沿海地区产生时速97公里的强风<ref name="mwr" />，倒塌的树木将一幢房屋摧毁<ref>{{cite report | author = Tenenbaum | work = Boston Weather Bureau Airway Station | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1962-08-30 | title = Preliminary Report on Hurricane Alma | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshbos.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120302215513/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/pshbos.gif | archivedate = 2012-03-02 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。马萨诸塞州的风暴潮高0.6米，引起轻度沿海洪灾，还有上百艘船被阿尔玛激起的大浪摧毁。整场风暴在新英格兰造成的经济损失估计不足100万美元，当地此前正逢旱灾，所以飓风产生的降水颇具助益。<ref name="mwr" />北面远至[[新罕布什尔|新罕布什尔]][[朴次茅斯_(新罕布什尔州)|朴次茅斯]]都因气旋影响受到破坏，降雨范围则向北延伸至缅因州境内。路面湿滑还引发多起交通事故，<ref name="bos">{{cite report | author = Edward Sable, Boston Weather Bureau Airway Station | date = 1962-09-12 | title = Summary of Tropical Storm Alma | accessdate = 2017-02-08 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/bos1107c.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1962/alma/preloc/bos1107c.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>但没有造成人员丧生。远离新英格兰后，阿尔玛在北面[[高气压|高气压天气系统]]影响下转向东南，最终于8月30日转变成温带气旋。<ref name="mwr" />
