8月26日，[[坦皮科|坦皮科]]东北方向约450公里的墨西哥湾西部发展出热带低气压。气旋围绕高压脊缓慢朝西北偏北移动，风速始终未能超过每小时45公里，并且一直受到[[风切变|风切变]]的不利影响，致使对流从中心向东北偏移。8月29日，气旋从德克萨斯州和路易斯安那州边界以西不远处登陆，最终于8月30日逐渐消散。德克萨斯州的降水很少，估计只有25毫米左右。路易斯安那州降下暴雨，并以[[卡梅伦堂区_(路易斯安那州)|卡梅伦堂区]][[哈克贝里_(路易斯安那州)|哈克贝里]]（{{lang|en|Hackberry}}）附近雨量最高，达588毫米。降雨范围还向东北方向延伸到[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]和[[密苏里州|密苏里州]]。<ref name="hurdat">{{cite web | author = Davd M. Roth | year = 2011 | title = CLIQR Database | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/ebtrk_nhc_final.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160713203832/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/ebtrk_nhc_final.txt | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | archivedate = 2016-07-13 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | date = 2009-09-22 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | title = Tropical Depression - August 28-31, 1962 | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/augusttd1962.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222033459/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/augusttd1962.html | archivedate = 2014-12-22 }}</ref>8月29日气旋上岸期间降下暴雨，在[[卡梅伦_(路易斯安那州)|卡梅伦]]引发街道洪灾。当地出现两场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，其中一场的风速达到每小时130公里。<ref name="ap829" />风暴令115套房屋或拖车受到破坏，其中一套被毁。气旋共夺走三条人命，还造成30人受伤，其中18人需前往医院治疗<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1962-08-30 | title = Louisiana Town Begins Cleanup Job | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Wz5QAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_1YDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5687,5238413&dq=louisiana+storm&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105202656/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Wz5QAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_1YDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5687%2C5238413&dq=louisiana+storm&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ap829">{{cite news | author = Staff writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1962-08-29 | newspaper = Toledo Blade | title = Storm Kills 3 in Louisiana | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=v7lOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MQEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4838,5171004&dq=louisiana&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105202659/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=v7lOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MQEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4838%2C5171004&dq=louisiana&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
