9月20日，一股[[冷心低压|冷心低压]]在佛罗里达州西岸近海催生出热带低气压。气旋以非常缓慢的速度向西北偏北移动，该州[[那不勒斯_(佛罗里达州)|那不勒斯]]至[[坦帕_(佛罗里达州)|坦帕]]地区降下暴雨，其中[[萨拉索塔_(佛罗里达州)|萨拉索塔]]雨量最高，达422毫米。降雨范围还向北延伸到乔治亚州和南卡罗莱纳州最南部，降雨量在25毫米以上。受南、北卡罗莱纳州近海逐渐发展的气旋影响，热带低气压于9月23日消散。<ref name="hurdat" /><ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | date = 2012-04-08 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | title = Tropical Depression - September 20-23, 1962 | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/septtd1962.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065447/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/septtd1962.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>

萨拉索塔的降雨量创下1945年后新高<ref name="922ap">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | title = Florida Makes Survey of Damage from Rainstorm | newspaper = The Reading Eagle | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=kxUrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eJwFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4038,3325359&dq=florida+storm&hl=en | date = 1962-09-22 | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105202753/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=kxUrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eJwFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4038%2C3325359&dq=florida+storm&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，部分地点甚至达到百年一遇水平<ref name="usgs">{{cite web | title = Report on Flood of 20-21 September 1962 Southwest Florida | date = 1962-11 | publisher = United States Army Corps of Engineers | url = http://www.tampabay.wateratlas.usf.edu/upload/documents/Rpt%20Flodd%2020-2i%20Sept%2062%20SW%20FL.pdf | accessdate = 2017-02-10 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040507/http://www.tampabay.wateratlas.usf.edu/upload/documents/Rpt%20Flodd%2020-2i%20Sept%2062%20SW%20FL.pdf }}</ref>。降水令佛罗里达州西部大范围地区发生洪灾，水深达0.9米<ref name="ap921">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1962-09-21 | title = Storm Swamps Florida as Frost Nips New England | newspaper = The Modesto Bee}}</ref>，[[海牛河|海牛河]]（{{lang|en|Manatee River}}）和菲利皮溪（{{lang|en|Phillippi Creek}}）的浪头高度创下新纪录。超过5000幢房屋进水，<ref name="usgs" />上百户居民被迫转移，另有三个县的学校被迫关闭<ref name="922ap" />。此外，洪水还对六个县的数千英亩农田构成影响，部分地点的积水数周后仍未退去<ref name="usgs" />。佛罗里达州东部的阵风时速达到93公里，超过两万人家中停电<ref name="922ap" />。整场风暴共导致该州一人丧生，损失数额估计达278万美元<ref name="usgs" />。
